summary: Dumai Dunai: Montreal-based Eclectic Band Bringing Dub Grooves and Punk Energy - Montreal-based Dumai Dunai has an eclectic sound, combining deep grooves of dub and energy of punk rock with ancient Slavic singing styles and Balkan wedding brass bands. Lead singers Natalia Telentso and Eli Camilo sing in multiple languages. The band has performed at various festivals and shared the stage with notable artists.
